name: libmkfs_ufs
desc:
This library comes from the `newfs` utility, which is installed by default in the aquaBSD core base. You can find it at `sbin/newfs/mkfs.c`.
A manpage is coming soon!
This library will probably be integrated into base at some point.

WWW: https://github.com/inobulles/aquabsd-core/tree/main/sbin/newfs
